entries.femaleVariant: First thing you gotta get is a neural blocker. Blocks your memories. Won't last two millisecs in the biz without it.
I dunno, I heard some people turned theirs on, never woke up.
Eh, it's all bullshit. Never heard 'bout anyone who didn't wake up eventually.
I mean, I read about a girl in Japan whose implant even blocked--
Look, it's like one of those dreams you forget soon as you wake up.
But how do you wake up?
You're gone, then – poof! – you're back in this shithole, few more eds in your pocket
It's like… like you got an alarm set. One moment you're out, the next you're back. Sometimes switch mine on when I need a break, ha ha ha.
